Troubleshooting Tips
Issue 1: Jailbreak Script Fails
Symptoms: Script exits with errors or doesn't update device status

Solutions:

Verify Python 3 is installed: python3 --version
Check file permissions: chmod +x tools/checkra1n-sim.py
Ensure device-status.txt exists in the correct directory
Review script output for specific error messages
Issue 2: SSH Connection Fails
Symptoms: Cannot establish SSH connection to device

Solutions:

Verify device is jailbroken: cat device-status.txt
Check device IP address matches configuration
Ensure SSH status shows ENABLED
Verify credentials (default: root/alpine)
Issue 3: Reports Not Generated
Symptoms: No files in reports/ directory

Solutions:

Create reports directory: mkdir -p reports
Check script has write permissions
Verify assessment script completed successfully
Review logs for error messages: cat logs/*.log
